                    <div>
                        <span class="suggestion-chip" onclick="askQuestion('What career is best for someone with programming skills?')">Best career for programmers</span>
                        <span class="suggestion-chip" onclick="askQuestion('What skills should I learn for data science?')">Data science skills</span>
                        <span class="suggestion-chip" onclick="askQuestion('What is the salary for software developers?')">Software developer salary</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
